{"tid":1424794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八月十號嘅大埔遊行，請準備大埔住宿，因為對外撤離有難度","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:38:26.000Z","uid":136686,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2b996cbc19d99967983781033604391e8efb2395","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"先講結論：<br />\n大埔對外巴士幾乎全停，警方可以用六個Road Block完全封殺對外車路<br />\n佢可以封到連校巴都入唔到去<br />\n只能經火車撤退，當火車都停埋（特別車你敢唔敢坐？）就只能夠係大埔過夜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZZ1BsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZZ1BsH.jpg&h=cbfdcd99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我住係大埔<br />\n雖然大埔好黃，但對外交通主要都係吐露港公路同火車，而舊路入口係吐露港公路隔離<br />\n經過八月五日嘅經驗，大埔一開波所有巴士都會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即刻停</span>，除左去大尾督嘅７５Ｋ改由太和做終點<br />\n（我當日係大中，但聽係太和同大埔墟嘅手足講係完全停曬）<br />\n我諗紅綠Van都差唔多收皮，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算有都車唔走咁多人</span><br />\n如果停埋火車大埔連埋太和係會即刻變左個孤島<br />\n<br />\n如果諗住坐車走<br />\n大埔有三個出口，用6個Road Block就可以完全封鎖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umKEn4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumKEn4h.jpg&h=2bbe6b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南行吐露港公路（包括隔離嘅山路&mdash;大埔公路）<br />\n有三條路線：<br />\n１廣福邨迴旋處出口<br />\n可以入吐露港公路同埋大埔公路<br />\n同一條路兩個分叉位，一個RoadBlock搞掂<br />\n最有效嘅RoadBlock位沒有第二<br />\n<br />\n２元洲公園近廣福邨車路<br />\n汀角路進吐露港的位置，因為隔離就係迴旋處，所以經常被忽視<br />\n<br />\n３運頭道<br />\n運頭塘邨隔離有個位上高速公路，唔係住係運頭塘（或者你好似我咁睇地圖）基本上唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n北行吐露港公路<br />\n１係太和直接上高速公路<br />\n２經大埔公路上高速公路，林棉公路或者大窩西支路（去粉領舊路）<br />\n兩者同樣會經過太和官小對開嘅十字路口<br />\n只要用兩個RoadBlock就可以封曬<br />\n<br />\n經汀角路路過工業邨外圍，入大尾督，新娘潭，再入沙頭角然後去上水<br />\n基本上係條一本道，除左有條分叉路去教育大學<br />\n不過警察可以係未到教大前嘅位Set RoadBlock，截斷教大嘅物資或者校車（好大機會咁做）<br />\n但如果入到教大嘅話都應該係安全嘅撤退點，但離戰區唔係用腳行到嘅距離<br />\n只要封左Lee6個街口，再封埋火車，大埔同太和就真係出唔到去<br />\n<br />\n不過好在大埔夠黃，好多人願意接濟義士同開門比佢地入屋苑<br />\n而且大埔係新界北總部，其他區嘅狗車有唔少都係大埔開嘅<br />\n如果可以拖住佢地就會有一堆狗車開唔到<br />\n所以大埔係有一定戰略意義，但要有係大埔過夜嘅準備<br />\n而且大埔／太和區本身唔算太細，就算出唔到去都有好多位可以走<br />\n除左唔好入富亨（三面環山嘅死位，但吹山風有利催淚彈煙消散）<br />\n<br />\n實際上要點樣做呢？都係跟現埸指示同埋哨兵情報啦。"},{"pid":"1b1dd95f57eee9fe10c2bd7e4004631bc7a2e020","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0562061a32a9af8741633d35a0e550c9e71dd6d","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"我係大埔人, 建議勇武唔好入大埔, 支援黃大仙<br />\n因為大埔和理非多, 支援不足, 地形又不利勇武<br />\n大埔遊行交返比和理非人算啦"},{"pid":"231b36e5b7098d386cfa282fb69cbb19db0093e1","tid":1424794,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"單車有冇得唸"},{"pid":"5fdaeb12d7c2b5bc89d7bfcb14639a60db045601","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231b36e5b7098d386cfa282fb69cbb19db0093e1","tid":1424794,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"單車有冇得唸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"封單車路咪仲易"},{"pid":"0367f1968c5693f27da4933ef6ac95b29fad9d48","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fdaeb12d7c2b5bc89d7bfcb14639a60db045601","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231b36e5b7098d386cfa282fb69cbb19db0093e1","tid":1424794,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"單車有冇得唸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"封單車路咪仲易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"踏單車出沙田或者粉嶺都好遠<br />\n起碼要一個鐘，條路仲要無咩登"},{"pid":"eef6db8e4855bb9ecc82431287e24f0c22141b22","tid":1424794,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"俾人困死就隨時真係得爬山，八仙嶺、大帽山有幾好行<br />\n行山撚都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975a992849a24e2025095b41c38a579276522db2","tid":1424794,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0562061a32a9af8741633d35a0e550c9e71dd6d","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"我係大埔人, 建議勇武唔好入大埔, 支援黃大仙<br />\n因為大埔和理非多, 支援不足, 地形又不利勇武<br />\n大埔遊行交返比和理非人算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a32db0002d999bb6a4de29889af0bfcbc2dab09","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"訓左一教返黎<br />\n就算警察可以全封大埔/太和<br />\n都有辦法上到私家車走佬<br />\n<br />\n但要行/踏單車好遠路<br />\n<br />\n1林村<br />\n林村多外姓人，唔似元朗咁多圍村佬<br />\n（我阿媽話嘅，自行判斷）<br />\n2康樂園<br />\n兩個地方都可以經大埔頭行過去，但路程唔短<br />\n<br />\n3科學園<br />\n行吐露港單車路出科學園<br />\n但單車路係條一本道，容易被夾"},{"pid":"ee2f8f9272834e9adb8e2a60e8c7bb29d84e8e64","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c9c7bf096a2991b04506519677758f90e604f8","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1574f74f95f88443e945e0e7c9796ffe9405d66","tid":1424794,"uid":105363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"用心睇下 PUSH"},{"pid":"2541fc0ca9260b37636247cf00b818e7d15a50e1","tid":1424794,"uid":203799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"真心推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3adc20135697507215f76f265b47844c5daebb1","tid":1424794,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a26884c6bdaa8874e8c75a4b439739828de72cc","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"8月5號一開波巴士就全封<br />\n公共交通得番火車走到<br />\n<br />\n而大埔/太和車路本身易set rb封公路出口<br />\n好難接放學<br />\n<br />\n所以一係入夜前散水<br />\n一係係大埔過夜"},{"pid":"3a5a1b6e4f1532b504bb815f2e2c5ae14002987f","tid":1424794,"uid":105363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"最好係入夜前散水<br />\n大埔既地勢真係不利"},{"pid":"b282ea364c5d28cde9e8d630376c3ae305ba05d9","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a5a1b6e4f1532b504bb815f2e2c5ae14002987f","tid":1424794,"uid":105363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"最好係入夜前散水<br />\n大埔既地勢真係不利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"大埔入面有好多位走<br />\n只係我諗唔到點出大埔外面"},{"pid":"50303336f2daedef65ee84e5885f29c6db276def","tid":1424794,"uid":175799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0367f1968c5693f27da4933ef6ac95b29fad9d48","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fdaeb12d7c2b5bc89d7bfcb14639a60db045601","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231b36e5b7098d386cfa282fb69cbb19db0093e1","tid":1424794,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"單車有冇得唸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"封單車路咪仲易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"踏單車出沙田或者粉嶺都好遠<br />\n起碼要一個鐘，條路仲要無咩登"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"夜晚踩去粉嶺 無記錯好似要過幾次天橋 唔熟可能唔識路<br />\n出沙田去一條大直路 到科學園就隧道陣x2 不過可以行出公園然後踩馬路<br />\n<br />\n但發完夢仲踩唔踩到10k都成問題"},{"pid":"55181a9243da97bbdbcb5be41563825471b6ba36","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50303336f2daedef65ee84e5885f29c6db276def","tid":1424794,"uid":175799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0367f1968c5693f27da4933ef6ac95b29fad9d48","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fdaeb12d7c2b5bc89d7bfcb14639a60db045601","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"封單車路咪仲易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"踏單車出沙田或者粉嶺都好遠<br />\n起碼要一個鐘，條路仲要無咩登"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"夜晚踩去粉嶺 無記錯好似要過幾次天橋 唔熟可能唔識路<br />\n出沙田去一條大直路 到科學園就隧道陣x2 不過可以行出公園然後踩馬路<br />\n<br />\n但發完夢仲踩唔踩到10k都成問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"踏到去科學園或林村可能有校巴搭到<br />\n但離主戰場好遠"},{"pid":"84dc797deadbd15eef86e973330b40e852d798e9","tid":1424794,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50303336f2daedef65ee84e5885f29c6db276def","tid":1424794,"uid":175799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0367f1968c5693f27da4933ef6ac95b29fad9d48","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fdaeb12d7c2b5bc89d7bfcb14639a60db045601","tid":1424794,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"封單車路咪仲易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"踏單車出沙田或者粉嶺都好遠<br />\n起碼要一個鐘，條路仲要無咩登"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"夜晚踩去粉嶺 無記錯好似要過幾次天橋 唔熟可能唔識路<br />\n出沙田去一條大直路 到科學園就隧道陣x2 不過可以行出公園然後踩馬路<br />\n<br />\n但發完夢仲踩唔踩到10k都成問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"單車徑會經過水警基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非去大學站，唔落到沙田"},{"pid":"adf0662e62eea4a284017ce3d1b2196d310fe615","tid":1424794,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d20111434c80d77454958db09be333d5157650","tid":1424794,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df92420e302383603784ee97b9e15fd88e8a088","tid":1424794,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf125446892bb849384b7e950366eaa1118c8f8b","tid":1424794,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"夜左真係要有過夜既準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4345bc525eb7d491e57c80c138dd2eaddde1e6","tid":1424794,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}